# Story 2.4: Show Maintenance Alerts

## Story Metadata
- **Epic:** 2 - Dashboard & KPIs
- **Status:** done
- **Implemented:** 2025-12-28
- **Session:** SESSION-004

## User Story
As **Gabriel (Fleet Manager)**,
I want **maintenance alerts on the dashboard**,
So that **I can see upcoming PM/HM requirements**.

## Acceptance Criteria

| AC | Criteria | Status |
|----|----------|--------|
| AC1 | Alerts for trains with maintenance in 7 days | PASS |
| AC2 | PM1, PM2, HM types distinguished | PASS |
| AC3 | Alert shows train ID and due date | PASS |
| AC4 | Alerts sorted by urgency | PASS |

## Implementation Details

### Files Created
- `apps/web/src/components/dashboard/MaintenanceAlerts.tsx` - Alert list component
- `apps/api/src/routes/dashboard.ts` - Added alerts endpoint

### Alert Logic
Calculates days until maintenance threshold:
- PM1: Every 50,000 km
- PM2: Every 150,000 km
- HM: Every 600,000 km

### UI Design
- List with severity badges (critical/warning/info)
- Train link to map view
- Collapsible for long lists

## Dev Notes
Alerts proactively surface maintenance needs.
Critical items (< 3 days) shown with red badge.

